fresh mountain air

132
00:07:27,666 --> 00:07:28,833
you can handle soon.

133
00:07:28,916 --> 00:07:30,875
Trust me, this location
is absolutely perfect

134
00:07:30,958 --> 00:07:33,333
for the script. Completely out
in the middle of nowhere.

135
00:07:33,416 --> 00:07:36,041
Isolated deep in the mountains,
and far away from people?

136
00:07:36,125 --> 00:07:37,541
So it really is a horror movie.

137
00:07:37,625 --> 00:07:38,666
[MIYAKE laughs]

138
00:07:38,750 --> 00:07:40,416
Come on, don't be an idiot.

139
00:07:40,500 --> 00:07:42,583
Sounds like you
touched a nerve. Ha.

140
00:07:42,666 --> 00:07:46,541
[FUCHI giggles]

141
00:07:46,625 --> 00:07:50,416
[ALL nervously gasp]

142
00:07:50,500 --> 00:07:52,083
[laughs]

143
00:07:52,166 --> 00:07:53,958
[GUY FRIEND A gasps]

144
00:07:54,041 --> 00:07:57,583
[laughing continues]

145
